Package com.jscape.inet.vfs

Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jscape.inet.vfs.Account
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.jscape.util.db.IntVersioned, java.io.Serializable
    public class Account
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, com.jscape.util.db.IntVersioned
    Represents user account abstraction. The account is a named block of user available files. It also contains basic user information.
    Author:
    Alex Usun
